  m_Text: 'In this area, you can play with UI items and see how values are synchronized
    in a VRChat world. Most of the items on the right will only be updated when they
    are changed by the Master of the world, who is the first person to enter the world.


    The exception is the ''UIButton Anyone'' - if someone clicks on this, they will
    soon become the Owner of the button, which will enable them to update the number
    for everyone else by clicking on it.'
